  <div style="display:flex;gap:0.8rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:1.5rem 0">
    <img loading="lazy" src="/images/mahjong-ways/mahjong-ways_multiplier-x2.webp" alt="麻將胡了 倍數 x2" style="width:100%;max-width:220px;height:auto;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border)" width="540" height="960">
    <img loading="lazy" src="/images/mahjong-ways/mahjong-ways_multiplier-x3.webp" alt="麻將胡了 倍數 x3" style="width:100%;max-width:220px;height:auto;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border)" width="540" height="960">
    <img loading="lazy" src="/images/mahjong-ways/mahjong-ways_multiplier-x5.webp" alt="麻將胡了 倍數 x5 大獎 50" style="width:100%;max-width:220px;height:auto;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--border)" width="540" height="960">
  </div>
  <p class="article-img-caption">▲ 倍數連鎖實戰：x2→x3→x5，消除到第 4 輪直接跳 x5，獎金從小到噴</p>

  <p>每一次旋轉開始時，盤面上方會顯示<strong>倍數指示器</strong>，初始為 x1。每一輪消除掉落的中獎都會讓倍數往上跳一級：</p>
  <h3>基礎遊戲倍數</h3>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>輪次</th><th>倍數</th><th>觸發條件</th></tr></thead>
